ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20that%20was%20driven%20by%20that%20image%20of%20how%20cool%20it%20would%20be%20if%20I%20were%20this%20person%20already%20working%20out%20of%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22890%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Wu%20outside%20BDO's%20Sydney%20headquarters%20in%202013.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c873d7c72ebc54a40e361d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22890%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELily%20Wu%20did%20a%20cadetship%20at%20the%20accounting%20firm%20BDO%20in%20Sydney%20in%202013.%20She%20said%20it%20didn't%20match%20her%20personality.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lily%20Wu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%2C%20at%20that%20point%2C%20I%20didn't%20really%20understand%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275b2b7ef-c5c2-4cda-9691-7d7f717e0895%5C%22%3ETesting%20my%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20really%20needed%20to%20explore%20and%20try%20out%20different%20options%20to%20see%20what%20resonated%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20accounting%20experience%2C%20I%20co-founded%20an%20education%20startup%20at%2019%2C%20running%20global%20career%20boot%20camps%20for%20university%20students.%20That%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20seven-figure%20business.%20I%20was%2024%20when%20I%20exited%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20whether%20I%20wanted%20to%20join%20a%20company%20like%20Facebook%20or%20Google%2C%20but%20something%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20to%20learn%20five%20languages%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%202019%2C%20there%20was%20no%20Covid%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20remote%20work%2C%20or%20it%20was%20very%2C%20very%20rare%2C%20and%20so%20working%20at%20Google%20or%20Facebook%20would%20limit%20my%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20choosing%20to%20work%20for%20a%20very%20young%20startup%2C%20and%20I%20helped%20them%20raise%20their%20