0by%2018%25%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20Tech-heavy%20growth%20stocks%20continue%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fai-stocks-stock-market-outlook-artificial-intelligence-economy-worker-shortage-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elead%20the%20gains%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20for%20good%20reason%3A%20AI%20and%20its%20transformative%20nature%20have%20consistently%20delivered%20outsized%20revenue%20growth%20with%20strong%20profit%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20performance%20has%20made%20them%20the%2021st-century%20definition%20of%20quality%2C%20says%20Dave%20Mazza%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Roundhill%20Investments.%20But%20on%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20it%20has%20pushed%20deep-value%20stocks%20that%20are%20significantly%20discounted%20out%20of%20favor%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20while%20many%20investors%20continue%20to%20chase%20the%20momentum%2C%20Wall%20Street's%20smart%20money%20is%20shopping%20for%20the%20bargains%20that%20have%20been%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BValue%20investors%20have%20become%20the%20butt%20of%20many%20jokes%20because%20they've%20suffered%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades%2C%20of%20underperformance%20relative%20to%20growth%20managers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mazza%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20whether%20it%20simply%20takes%20a%20reversion%20to%20the%20mean%20or%20the%20environment%20economically%20begins%20to%20favor%20a%20broadening%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20more%20attractive%20time%20to%20enter%20the%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMazza%2C%20whose%20firm%20has%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-an-etf%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dtraded%2520fund)%253F-%2CAn%2520exchange%252Dtraded%2520fund%2520(ETF)%2520is%2520a%2520basket%2520of%2Cmarket%2520exchanges%2520through%2520brokerage%2520firms.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EETF%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tracks%20the%20Acquirers%20Deep%20Value%20Index%2C%20believes%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rate-cuts-wall-street-how-much-jackson-hole-fed-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20rate%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20be%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20remain%20the%20catalyst%20for%20a%20broader%20market%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20timing%20might%20be%20just%20right%3A%20According%20to%20an%20August%20note%2C%20the%20legendary%20investor%20Jeremy%20Grantham's%20investment%20firm%2C%20GMO%2C%20has%20pegged%20deep-value%20stocks%20in%20%26quot%3Bscreamingly%26quot%3B%20cheap%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cohort%20of%20stocks%20has%20now%20hit%20a%20four-decade%20low%2C%20or%20the%20cheapest%20since%201980%2C%20said%20Catherine%20LeGraw%2C%20an%20asset%20allocator%20at%20GMO.%20She%20added%20that%20deep%20value%2C%20which%20is%20the%20cheapest%2020%25%20of%20stocks%20they%20track%2C%20typically%20trade%20at%20a%2040%25%20discount%20to%20the%20market%20but%20are%20now%20at%20a%2053%25%20discount.%20Turning%20this%20part%20of%20the%20market%20into%20the%20firm's%20highest%20conviction%20bet%20for%20a%20long-term%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20when%20deep-value%20stocks%20have%20traded%20in%20ranges%20near%20this%20cheapness%2C%20they%20dramatically%20outperformed%20the%20market%20in%20a%20subsequent%20five-year%20period%20by%2019%25%20on%20an%20annualized%20basis%2C%20LeGraw%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20so%20unusual%20and%20interesting%20about%20value%20today%20is%20how%20much%20cheaper%20they%20are%20than%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20LeGraw%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20analysis%20looking%20at%20how%20unusual%20the%20market%20environment%20is%20today%20relative%20to%20history%2C%20and%20what%20we%20found%20is%20that%20value%20and%20deep%20value%20are%20trading%20in%20the%20bottom%20decile%20of%20their%20normal%20historical%20range.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221fba916f-a945-4ac5-b444-8b2a9e7d7cbf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20shop%20value%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20be%20fooled%20by%20the%20traditional%20markers%20of%20cheapness%20that%20tend%20to%20lean%20into%20low%20price-to-earnings%20multiples.%20Numbers%20don't%20tell%20the%20full%20story.%20A%20low%20P%2FE%20stock%20could%20be%20worth%20much%20less%20because%20of%20slowing%20profitability.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20higher%20P%2FE%20may%20warrant%20an%20even%20bigger%20premium.%20For%20GMO%2C%20it's%20about%20looking%20under%20the%20hood%20at%20a%20company's%20operations%20to%20determine%20whether%20it's%20consistently%20profitable%2C%20has%20a%20low%20debt%20load%2C%20good%20management%20behavior%2C%20and%20a%20solid%20growth%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20often%20this%20idea%20that%20momentum%20is%20only%20growth%2C%20but%20it's%20really%20just%20whatever%20has%20been%20doing%20well%2C%20says%20Kevin%20Gordon%2C%20a%20senior%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Charles%20Schwab.%20And%20there%20are%20times%20when%20deep%20value%20merges%20with%20momentum%2C%20and%20the%20two%20become%20one.%20This%20merger%20often%20happens%20when%20sectors%20come%20back%20after%20being%20left%20behind%20due%20to%20weaker%20economic%20conditions%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGordon%20noted%20that%20stocks%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20fall%20out%20of%20their%20traditional%20grouping%20in%20the%20post-pandemic%20era.%20So%2C%20if%20an%20investor%20is%20screening%20for%20value%20characteristics%20using%20metrics%20such%20as%20a%20low%20P%2FE%20ratio%2C%20high%20free%20cash%20flow%20yield%2C%20or%20high-interest%20coverage%2C%20they%20will%20more%20readily%20find%20stocks%20that%20meet%20the%20criteria%20in%20every%20sector%2C%20including%20tech%20and%20communication%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Alphabet%20and%20Meta%2C%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20growth%20stocks%2C%20now%20fall%20into%20GMO's%20deep%20value%20basket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20wary%20of%20the%20classic%20value%20traps%2C%20says%20Mazza.%20These%20are%20companies%20with%20deteriorating%20fundamentals%2C%20perhaps%20because%20their%20business%20models%20are%20broken%20or%20their%20industries%20are%20under%20pressure.%20They%20will%20look%20cheap%20but%20have%20no%20signs%20of%20growth%20or%20their%20growth%20isn't%20profitable%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20go%20the%20ETF%20route%2C%20Gordon%20cautions%20against%20simply%20piling%20into%20any%20value-labeled%20fund.%20It's%20important%20to%20know%20how%20they%20filter%20for%20value.%20Funds%20that%20use%20simplistic%20multiples%20may%20miss%20the%20mark.%20Instead%2C%20they%20should%20use%20several%20criteria.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20in%20a%20higher%20interest%20rate%20environment%20that%20may%20remain%20elevated%20for%20some%20time%2C%20he%20added.%20He%20advises%20sticking%20to%20stocks%20with%20higher%20free%20cash%20flow%20yields%20and%20higher%20interest%20coverage%20ratios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20how%20aggressively%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20cuts%20rates%20will%20also%20impact%20value's%20performance%20in%20the%20coming%20year%2C%20Gordon%20noted.%20If%20the%20cutting%20is%20slow%20and%20gradual%2C%20it%20means%20the%20economy%20remains%20strong.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20value-oriented%20cyclicals%20like%20financials%2C%20energy%2C%20industrials%2C%20and%20materials%20can%20do%20well.%20Conversely%2C%20if%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20aggressively%20in%20response%20to%20recessionary%20fears%2C%20value-based%20cyclicals%20will%20likely%20underperform%20given%20potential%20economic%20weakness.%20The%20good%20news%20is%2C%20Gordon%20believes%20the%20former%20scenario%20is%20more%20likely%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-smart-money-buying-deep-value-how-to-invest-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725012004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%