't%20have%20a%20history%20of%20working%20together%20at%20scale%20in%20this%20sort%20of%20context.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20them%20don't%20have%20it%20in%20their%20capabilities%20or%20mission%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20the%20kind%20of%20attack%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20are%20putting%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20Russia's%20response%20in%20action%2C%20Ukraine's%20troops%20are%20still%20advancing%20into%20Kursk%2C%20although%20at%20a%20much%20slower%20rate%20as%20resistance%20builds%2C%20even%20amid%20Russia's%20poor%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de7f9b00-b2dc-4feb-9f99-332f8a489daf%5C%22%3ERussia%20is%20downplaying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20downplaying%20Ukraine's%20invasion%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20terrorist%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20men%20in%20suits%20sit%20around%20the%20end%20of%20a%20rectangular%20black%20table%20with%20a%20cream%20wall%2C%20a%20coat%20of%20arms%2C%20and%20the%20Russian%20flag%20behind%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b492095da406397bf41711%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20sits%20with%20defense%20officials%20%E2%80%94%20Director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Security%20Service%20(FSB)%20Alexander%20Bortnikov%2C%20Security%20Council's%20Secretary%20Sergei%20Shoigu%2C%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20Andrei%20Belousov%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20meeting%20about%20Ukraine's%20incursion%20into%20the%20Kursk%20region%20on%20August%207%2C%202024.%3Cp%3ESputnik%2FAleksey%20Babushkin%2FKremlin%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBarros%20said%20that%20Putin%20has%20not%20taken%20a%20stronger%20step%2C%20like%20declaring%20martial%20law%2C%20as%20he%20wants%20to%20minimize%20political%20risk%20to%20himself.%20Throughout%20Putin's%20invasion%2C%20which%20bega