reports%20have%20also%20said%20he%20would%20illegally%20arrange%20hospital%20beds%20and%20other%20facilities%20for%20patients%20in%20exchange%20for%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20also%20emerged%20as%20a%20massive%20political%20challenge%20for%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20and%20the%20Left%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20Bengal%20has%20also%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20its%20ally%20Congress.%20Commenting%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20attempt%20to%20save%20the%20accused%2C%20instead%20of%20providing%20justice%20to%20the%20victim%2C%20raises%20serious%20questions%20on%20the%20hospital%20and%20the%20local%20administration%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725002520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkk1vhpcc_mamata-banerjee_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-rajnath-singh-mamata-banerjee-not-sincere-efforts-bjps-swipe-at-bengal-government-over-murder-probe-6451112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20that%20many%20states%20are%20not%20sincere%20about%20tackling%20the%20rising%20crimes%20against%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-rajnath-singh-mamata-banerjee-not-sincere-efforts-bjps-swipe-at-bengal-government-over-murder-probe-6451112%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20to%20release%20iPhone%20intelligence%20features%20in%20batches%3A%20Check%20timeline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725002111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2