ofessor%20in%20a%20government%20college%20in%20Sonipat.%20She%20takes%20care%20of%20all%20of%20the%20household%20expenses%20and%20often%20takes%20time%20off%20to%20teach%20the%20children.%20I%20am%20so%20grateful%20to%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Amit%2C%20about%20five%20fellow%20officers%20and%20former%20students%20spare%20time%20to%20teach%20the%20students.%20Sonu%2C%20who%20works%20with%20the%20Delhi%20police%20and%20teaches%20English%20and%20General%20Knowledge%20to%20students%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20working%20with%20Amit%20sir%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20I%20have%20witnessed%20his%20struggles.%20He%20is%20a%20selfless%20and%20dedicated%20individual.%20I%20am%20glad%20to%20be%20part%20of%20his%20cause.%20I%20also%20dedicate%202-3%20days%20in%20a%20week%20to%20teach%20students%20when%20Amit%20sir%20is%20on%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20holistic%20development%20and%20encourages%20children%20to%20explore%20various%20paths%20to%20success.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20some%20children%20secure%20government%20jobs%2C%20some%20choose%20to%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20to%20do%20farming%20after%20unsuccessful%20attempts.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20them%20self-reliant%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20activities%20in%20greed%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20perseverance%20and%20selfless%20dedication%2C%20Amit%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20On%20his%20commitment%20to%20providing%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20received%20multiple%20awards%20for%20this%20work.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20work%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Epuraskar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(award)%20but%20for%20%3Cem%3Epurushartha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(purpose%20of%20human%20being).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C