ioned%20to%20growing%20a%20variety%20of%20essential%20vegetables%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20chillies%2C%20cherry%20tomatoes%2C%20beans%2C%20cucumbers%2C%20brinjals%2C%20curry%20leaves%2C%20cauliflowers%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20more.%20With%20over%20200%20plants%20thriving%20in%20grow%20bags%2C%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348771%2Fgrow-organic-food-doctor-naveen-kumar-farming-workshop-chennai-vegetables-fruits-at-home-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20terrace%20garden%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20joy%20and%20sustenance%20for%20Padma%3B%20and%20also%20a%20link%20to%20her%20rural%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20have%20to%20purchase%20potatoes%2C%20garlic%2C%20tamarind%2C%20and%20onions%20from%20the%20market.%20Other%20than%20these%20vegetables%2C%20my%20terrace%20garden%20supplies%20all%20the%20basic%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Padma%20grows%20veggies%20such%20as%20chillies%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20beans%2C%20brinjals%2C%20curry%20leaves%2C%20cauliflowers%2C%20okra%2C%20and%20more.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-suresh-1-1724831341-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fpadma-sur