an%20impetus%20to%20the%20artisans%20in%20the%20area%20who%20earn%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F253969%2Freshamandi-agri-tech-startup-silk-farmers-karnataka-mayank-tiwari-utkarsh-apoorv-nift-sericulture-mulberry-iot-ai-business-technology-agriculture-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilk%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20turning%20the%20silk%20into%20textiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPractising%20what%20they%20preach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeka%20and%20Meynell%20shy%20away%20from%20making%20bold%20statements%20about%20their%20sustainable%20endeavours.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20it%20more%20as%20a%20set%20of%20lifestyle%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deka%20notes.%20Instead%20of%20positioning%20Medini%20Homestay%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98idyllic%20sustainable%20spot%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20dare%20to%20contradict%20conventional%20approaches%E2%80%99%2C%20Deka%20says%20it%20is%20instead%2C%20a%20simple%20passion%20project%20for%20anyone%20looking%20to%20have%20a%20slice%20of%20nature%20with%20their%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20at%20Medini%20Homestay%2C%20he%20insists.%20Even%20himself.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20still%20learning%20the%20ways%20of%20farming.%E2%80%9D%20In%202018%2C%20when%20Deka%20stared%20at%20the%20piece%20of%20land%20he%20now%20calls%20home%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20confident.%20The%20task%20of%20creating%20something%20beautiful%20out%20of%20the%20barren%20woodland%20felt%20daunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-8-1724335945.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deka%20has%20cultivated%20a%20forest%20in%20the%20once%20barren%20land.%20There%20are%20now%20over%2