w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Assamese%20culture%20is%20reflected%20through%20events%20at%20the%20homestay%20and%20the%20food.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20grey%20water%20from%20the%20kitchens%20is%20treated%20through%20a%20natural%20reed%20bed%20made%20with%20stones%2C%20sand%2C%20and%20a%20natural%20reed%20bed%2C%20which%20purifies%20the%20water%20before%20it%20returns%20to%20the%20natural%20groundwater.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20amazing%20the%20oasis%20of%20green%20choices%20that%20the%20couple%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20creating%20with%20no%20prior%20background%20in%20agriculture.%20As%20Deka%20walks%20into%20the%20fields%20for%20yet%20another%20evening%20of%20conversing%20with%20his%20plants%2C%20his%20years%20of%20underwater%20diving%20seem%20well%20behind%20him.%20The%20sea%20of%20green%20is%20where%20he%20belongs!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EPicture%20credits%3A%20Champak%20Deka%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724338206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-2-1724335335.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Medini%20Homestay%20in%20Bokakhat%2C%20Assam%2C%20is%20a%20sustainable%20retreat%20created%20by%20couple%20Champak%20Deka%20and%20Anna-Louise%20Meynell.%20Over%20six%20years%2C%20they%20have%20transformed%20a%20barren%20patch%20of%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20green%20oasis%2C%20promoting%20cruelty-free%20silk%20production%20and%20eco-friendly%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362584%2Fmedini-homestay-kaziranga-national-park-assam-sustainable-champak-deka-anna-louise-meynell%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Organise%20Food%20Drives%20in%20India%3F%205-Step%20Guide%20From%20a%20Man%20Providing%203000%20Free%20Meals%20Weekly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20afternoon%2C%20hundreds%20of%20daily-wage%20labourers%20flock%20to%20the%20bustling%20Nahariya%20circle%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20sparing%20some%20time%20for%20lunch%20in%20an%20exhausting%20work%20day.%20There%2C%20they%20meet%20Somnath%20Kashyap%20eagerly%20awaiting%20to%20hand%20over%20their%20share%20of%20%3Cem%3Epuri%20sabzi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(bread%20with%20curry).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20college%20days%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20Somnath%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20driven%20by%20a%20simple%20yet%20powerful%20realisation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20distressing%20sight%20of%20food%20wastage%20versus%20the%20glaring%20need%20for%20it%20amongst%20the%20underprivileged%20labourers%20in%20his%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20friend%2C%20who%20was%20a%20caterer%2C%20often%20told%20me%20about%20the%20excess%20food%20they%20had%20to%20throw%20away%20after%20weddings%20and%20events.%20One%20night%2C%20he%20called%20me%20to%20come%20and%20collect%20the%20leftover%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20big%20containers.%20I%20took%20three%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20somehow%20managed%20to%20keep%20those%20large%20pots%20on%20our%20scooters%20and%20went%20to%20distribute%20the%20food.%20It%20was%20a%20little%20challenging%20on%20the%20first%20day%20as%20we%20had%20an%20overwhelming%20number%20of%20people%2C%20but%20it%20was%20so%20satisfying%20to%20see%20them%20relish%20that%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFueled%20by%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%20Somnath%2C%20a%20content%20writer%20by%20profession%2C%20started